"{\"uid\": \"walesonline.co.uk-whats-on-travel-cheap-flights-paris-ahead-olympics-29381712\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Travel experts are urging Brits to make the most of \\\"incredibly cheap\\\" travel fares to Paris this month, before thousands visit the French capital ahead of the Olympics in July.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 177, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 87, \"end\": 92, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6528898522993526e-23, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 132, \"end\": 138, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.8635297678511039, \"rank\": 0.15764754994744112, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With last-minutereturn flightsfrom Manchester Airport to Paris Beauvais at just \\u00a327 with Ryanair and Vueling offering \\u00a357return flightsfrom London Gatwick to Paris Orly before the end of the month, now is the ideal time to bag a bargain trip to Paris, they said.\", \"from\": 178, \"to\": 440, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 213, \"end\": 231, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manchester_Airport\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.963146911440086e-16, \"text\": \"Manchester Airport\", \"types\": [\"Q1248784\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manchester_Airport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manchester_Airport\"}, {\"begin\": 235, \"end\": 240, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6528898522993526e-23, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 241, \"end\": 249, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beauvais\", \"score\": 0.999999999998181, \"rank\": 1.3031456913504033e-12, \"text\": \"Beauvais\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beauvais\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beauvais\"}, {\"begin\": 267, \"end\": 274, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryanair\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ryanair\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q46970\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryanair\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryanair\"}, {\"begin\": 318, \"end\": 332, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gatwick_Airport\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"London Gatwick\", \"types\": [\"Q1248784\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gatwick_Airport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gatwick_Airport\"}, {\"begin\": 336, \"end\": 346, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Orly_Airport\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Orly\", \"types\": [\"Q1248784\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Orly_Airport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Orly_Airport\"}, {\"begin\": 423, \"end\": 428, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6528898522993526e-23, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When it comes to the Eurostar, you can bookreturn ticketsfor less than \\u00a3100 if you travel before the Olympics start on July 26.\", \"from\": 442, \"to\": 569, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 463, \"end\": 471, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4084797887552106e-19, \"text\": \"Eurostar\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Laura Evans-Fisk, head of digital and engagement ateurochange, said: \\\"Paris is known as one of the most expensive cities in Europe and travelling to and from it usually does not come cheaply either.\", \"from\": 570, \"to\": 768, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 570, \"end\": 575, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Bush\", \"score\": 0.8161382359496102, \"rank\": 0.22526147737514549, \"text\": \"Laura\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Bush\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Bush\"}, {\"begin\": 640, \"end\": 645, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6528898522993526e-23, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So if you can save some money getting there, you should seize that opportunity.\", \"from\": 769, \"to\": 848, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In July through to September when the Olympics come to the French capital, travel, accommodation and public transport costs will almost skyrocket.\", \"from\": 850, \"to\": 997, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 910, \"end\": 916, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.8635297678511039, \"rank\": 0.15764754994744112, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"M\\u00e9tro tickets are set to double in price, with a book of 10 increasing from \\u20ac16.90 to \\u20ac32.\", \"from\": 998, \"to\": 1088, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The average hotel price is set toincrease by 92%andair fares by 21%.\\\"\", \"from\": 1090, \"to\": 1160, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Laura explained that now was also the best time to visit Paris ahead of the crowds descending on the city over the next few months.\", \"from\": 1161, \"to\": 1292, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1161, \"end\": 1166, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Bush\", \"score\": 0.8161382359496102, \"rank\": 0.22526147737514549, \"text\": \"Laura\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Bush\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Bush\"}, {\"begin\": 1218, \"end\": 1223, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6528898522993526e-23, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She said: \\\"Being a capital city, Paris is obviously never quiet, but the Olympics is expected to attract 15million tourists, which will almost certainly mean it will feel extremely crowded.\", \"from\": 1294, \"to\": 1483, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1327, \"end\": 1332, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6528898522993526e-23, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Visiting Paris during the Olympics would of course be an amazing experience, but my advice would be not to book anything last-minute.\", \"from\": 1484, \"to\": 1617, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1493, \"end\": 1498, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6528898522993526e-23, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Over50% of hotels across the whole of Franceare fully booked over this period, and the number is increasing daily.\", \"from\": 1619, \"to\": 1734, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you want to experience Paris without the crowds and price hikes, now is definitely the best time to visit.\\\"\", \"from\": 1735, \"to\": 1845, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1761, \"end\": 1766, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6528898522993526e-23, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For travellers visiting Paris over the next few months, whether it's for the Olympics or just before the event, Laura shares her budgeting tips to help you save your cash in the city.\", \"from\": 1847, \"to\": 2030, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1871, \"end\": 1876, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6528898522993526e-23, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1959, \"end\": 1964, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Bush\", \"score\": 0.8161382359496102, \"rank\": 0.22526147737514549, \"text\": \"Laura\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Bush\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Bush\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Get your travel money in advance  Laura said: \\\"Typically, the EUR rate only moves very slightly over any given month.\", \"from\": 2032, \"to\": 2149, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2066, \"end\": 2071, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Bush\", \"score\": 0.8161382359496102, \"rank\": 0.22526147737514549, \"text\": \"Laura\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Bush\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Bush\"}, {\"begin\": 2094, \"end\": 2097, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Euro\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.045163820066184e-40, \"text\": \"EUR\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Euro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Euro\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even when the exchange rate differs marginally when buying larger amounts, it can soon add up, so it's worth keeping a close eye on the exchange rate before you head to Paris.\", \"from\": 2150, \"to\": 2325, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2319, \"end\": 2324, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6528898522993526e-23, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I would always recommend buying your euros before you get to the airport or Eurostar train station, as the exchange rates tend to be far higher than when you buy in advance, in branch or online.\", \"from\": 2327, \"to\": 2522, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2404, \"end\": 2412, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4084797887552106e-19, \"text\": \"Eurostar\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Typically, Monday through to Thursday is the best time to buy your euros, as these are the least busy days for transfers, so you might see a little less fluctuation in the mid-market rate.\\\"\", \"from\": 2523, \"to\": 2712, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Use public transport, and buy your tickets in bulk  Laura said: \\\"It's a great idea to get hold of a weekly or monthly pass if you are planning to use public transport on your trip.\", \"from\": 2714, \"to\": 2894, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2766, \"end\": 2771, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Bush\", \"score\": 0.8161382359496102, \"rank\": 0.22526147737514549, \"text\": \"Laura\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Bush\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Bush\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This will help you save quite a bit of cash.\", \"from\": 2895, \"to\": 2939, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Although prices are set to increase for the Olympics, if you are going to be using public transport regularly, it will still be more cost-effective to buy in bulk.\", \"from\": 2940, \"to\": 3103, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The weekly and monthly travel passes are valid on all forms of public transport in the \\u00cele-de-France region, including M\\u00e9tro, RER, bus, tram and train, with the exception of the Orlyval, SNCF train lines with reserved seating, and the Optile special fare lines.\\\"\", \"from\": 3105, \"to\": 3368, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3193, \"end\": 3206, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2004_European_Parliament_election_in_France\", \"score\": 0.9999946185038618, \"rank\": 5.38062602412707e-06, \"text\": \"\\u00cele-de-France\", \"types\": [\"Q40231\", \"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2004_European_Parliament_election_in_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2004_European_Parliament_election_in_France\"}, {\"begin\": 3232, \"end\": 3235, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Exchange_rate\", \"score\": 0.8294415925383892, \"rank\": 0.2056294460249422, \"text\": \"RER\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Exchange_rate\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Exchange_rate\"}, {\"begin\": 3284, \"end\": 3291, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Orlyval\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Orlyval\", \"types\": [\"Q728937\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Orlyval\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Orlyval\"}, {\"begin\": 3341, \"end\": 3347, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Optile\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Optile\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Optile\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Optile\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rent a bicycle  Laura said: \\\"Paris is a very cycle-friendly city, and hopping on a bike is a great way to explore.\", \"from\": 3370, \"to\": 3484, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3399, \"end\": 3404, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6528898522993526e-23, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Use V\\u00e9lib', the city's bike-sharing system for short trips.\", \"from\": 3485, \"to\": 3544, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you are visiting during the Olympics, there may also be temporary bike rental services set up specifically for this period, so make sure to look out for those.\\\"\", \"from\": 3545, \"to\": 3708, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Avoid taxis and ride-sharing services  Laura said: \\\"Ubers and other taxi services will be in high demand over the next few months, particularly during the Olympics, so they are likely to have surge pricing.\", \"from\": 3710, \"to\": 3916, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3749, \"end\": 3754, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Bush\", \"score\": 0.8161382359496102, \"rank\": 0.22526147737514549, \"text\": \"Laura\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Bush\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Bush\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's best to avoid these if you can.\\\"\", \"from\": 3917, \"to\": 3954, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Book accommodation close to public transport stops  Laura said: \\\"A simple hack, but if you can, book accommodation that is near to the M\\u00e9tro, or a bus or tram stop.\", \"from\": 3956, \"to\": 4120, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4008, \"end\": 4013, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Bush\", \"score\": 0.8161382359496102, \"rank\": 0.22526147737514549, \"text\": \"Laura\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Bush\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Bush\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This will mean you can get around quicker, and you can rely on public transport rather than taxis.\\\"\", \"from\": 4121, \"to\": 4220, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Plan your routes in advance  Laura said: \\\"Use apps like CityMapper to find the most efficient and cost-effective routes before you head out sightseeing each day.\", \"from\": 4222, \"to\": 4383, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4251, \"end\": 4256, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Bush\", \"score\": 0.8161382359496102, \"rank\": 0.22526147737514549, \"text\": \"Laura\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Bush\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Bush\"}, {\"begin\": 4278, \"end\": 4288, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Citymapper\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"CityMapper\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Citymapper\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Citymapper\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris is a huge city, so it's also a good idea to stick to one particular area each day, rather than hopping from one side of the city to another.\\\"\", \"from\": 4384, \"to\": 4531, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4384, \"end\": 4389, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6528898522993526e-23, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"AtReach and across our entitieswe and our partners use information collected through cookies and other identifiers from your device to improve experience on our site, analyse how it is used and to show personalised advertising.\", \"from\": 4533, \"to\": 4760, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can opt out of the sale or sharing of your data, at any time clicking the \\\"Do Not Sell or Share my Data\\\" button at the bottom of the webpage.\", \"from\": 4761, \"to\": 4906, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please note that your preferences are browser specific.\", \"from\": 4907, \"to\": 4962, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Use of our website and any of our services represents your acceptance of the use ofcookiesand consent to the practices described in ourPrivacy NoticeandTerms and Conditions.\", \"from\": 4963, \"to\": 5136, \"entities\": []}]}"